root-tail: tail on the root window
root-tail:
root-tail: Root-tail is a program that allows printing of text directly
root-tail: to the X11 root window wherever you choose, much like running
root-tail: rxvt with 'tail -f' with a pixmap background but without the
root-tail: hassle and with more features like text shadowing and different
root-tail: colors for multiple log files.
root-tail:
